flowchart TD
    Start([ReportService.create]) --> Save[Создать запись reports PENDING]
    Save --> Dispatch[GenerateReportJob dispatch]
    Dispatch --> Job[Очередь Redis]
    Job --> Gen[ReportService.generate]
    Gen --> Proc[status PROCESSING]
    Proc --> Fetch[Выборка COMPLETED sails за период]
    Fetch --> XLSX[OpenSpout Writer XLSX]
    XLSX --> Ok{успех?}
    Ok -->|да| Done[status COMPLETED file path]
    Ok -->|нет| Fail[status FAILED]
